# canvas (an optional dependency of pdfjs-dist) is only used for Node-side
# PDF *rendering*, which this project never does — we extract text with
# pdf.js and render test images with pymupdf/reportlab. Skipping optional
# deps removes the canvas -> node-pre-gyp -> tar subtree (a dev-only tar
# advisory) and drops the native build toolchain requirement for a clean
# `npm install`. Nothing shipped to the browser is affected.
omit=optional
